snippet.title: Loneliest Depths -  Step inside your diving bell and venture into the deepest depths of the trench!
snippet.description:
Play for free on itch.io https://shallow-lagoon.itch.io/loneliest-depths?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt What mysteries await beneath the oceans surface?

Step inside your diving bell and venture into the deepest depths of the Bitter Maw Trench, encountering a vast array of dazzling ocean life and documenting your discoveries!

Press the central switch to engage the diving bell’s viewing lantern, providing high voltage florescent light to even the lowest depths of the ocean floor.

➡️ More from Spooky Lagoon https://shallow-lagoon.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
➡️ More horror games https://itch.io/games/tag-horror?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
